data.text:
An official state visit to Thailand by Princess Alexandra of Kent (1926-) - pictured with King Bhumibol Adulyadej (Rama IX) (1927-) and Queen Sirikit (1932-) of Thailand with their eldest daughter Princess Ubolratana Rajakanya (1951-) at the Chitlada Palace in Bangkok. Date: 1959. Mary Evans Picture Library makes available wonderful images created for people to enjoy over the centuries. Â© Illustrated London News Ltd/Mary Evans

Media ID 14393256
